Package: veganUtils
Type: Package
Title: Utility functions and extensions to vegan and ggvegan
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-0-23
Authors@R: c(person("Mikko", "Vihtakari", email = "mikko.vihtakari@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: veganUtils contains extensions and utility functions to vegan
    with the aim to make vegan graphics in ggplot2. 
    The package is complementary to ggvegan and attempts 
    to use ggvegan solutions whenever possible.  
Imports: vegan, ggvegan, ggplot2, ggrepel, reshape2, gridExtra
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
